From: Esteban Urrutia <esteuwu@proton.me>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 21:44:55 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 04/13] dt-bindings: phy: qcom,sc8280xp-qmp-usb43dp-phy: Add
 SM8475 QMP PHY

SM8450 init sequence for this PHY varies significantly and can't be used in SM8475.
Add proper init sequence and bindings for the PHY found in this SoC.
---
 .../devicetree/bindings/phy/qcom,sc8280xp-qmp-usb43dp-phy.yaml   | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/phy/qcom,sc8280xp-qmp-usb43dp-phy.yaml b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/phy/qcom,sc8280xp-qmp-usb43dp-phy.yaml
index 4eff92343ce4..b9d0de25f43c 100644
--- a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/phy/qcom,sc8280xp-qmp-usb43dp-phy.yaml
+++ b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/phy/qcom,sc8280xp-qmp-usb43dp-phy.yaml
@@ -37,6 +37,7 @@ properties:
           - qcom,sm8250-qmp-usb3-dp-phy
           - qcom,sm8350-qmp-usb3-dp-phy
           - qcom,sm8450-qmp-usb3-dp-phy
+          - qcom,sm8475-qmp-usb3-dp-phy
           - qcom,sm8550-qmp-usb3-dp-phy
           - qcom,sm8650-qmp-usb3-dp-phy
           - qcom,sm8750-qmp-usb3-dp-phy
